text: The Örgryte Old Church () is a church building in Örgryte in the town of Gothenburg in Sweden. It belongs to the Örgryte Parish of the Church of Sweden. A church at the present site of the Örgryte Old Church has been around since the 13th century. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Churches in Gothenburg Category:13th-century buildings and structures
title: Örgryte Old Church
